gnome-shell-extension-stage-manager (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Maximize-to-workspace: maximized windows move to new workspaces.
  * Stage Manager sidebar with live window thumbnails.
  * Configurable settings via GNOME Extensions preferences.
  * Supports GNOME 45-48, Wayland and X11.

 -- Stage Manager Contributors <stage-manager@example.com>  Sun, 15 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000
